cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper discusses the application of actor-critic reinforcement learning approach to control a nonlinear, complex and black-boxed system. This falls under the category of machine learning and robotics, which are covered by the sub-categories cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.AI, and cs.NE. Among these, cs.LG and cs.RO are the most likely categories as they deal with machine learning and robotics respectively. cs.SY is also likely as it covers control systems. cs.AI and cs.NE are less likely as they are broader categories that cover a wide range of topics in artificial intelligence and neural networks.
